" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 560px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Oblique fractures of the lateral and posterior malleoli",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 540px; height: 405px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    While the fracture of the lateral malleolus (white arrow) is clearly seen on both views, the posterior malleolar fracture (blue arrowhead) is only seen on the lateral view. This combination of injuries&nbsp;is unstable, as suggested by the widened medial joint line (blue arrow); orthopedic referral is needed.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
